ity enhancement (now the hot core) was impacted by\nshocks generated from an explosive event 500 yrs ago.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Sep 2017 23:19:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Jan 2018 23:00:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-04"}
