% absolute F1,\nrespectively. Finally, an ensemble of text and image classifiers further\nimproves the absolute F1 measure by 4% on average.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Sep 2017 02:06:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-01"}
