tween the current and the magnetic field which indicates the\nimproved quality of the force-free solution obtained by S-NLFFF.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Sep 2017 08:11:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-20"}
